OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged theft of
OL,4,Chip replacements from crematorium
OL,6,FPolice are investigating the alleged
OL,7,Ftheft of hip replacements from a
OL,8,Fcrematorium in Cardiff, with the
OL,9,Fcouncil confirming that an employee
OL,10,Fhas since been dismissed.
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police say an
OL,13,Finvestigation is "ongoing" after
OL,14,Forthopaedic implants were allegedly
OL,15,Fstolen from Thornhill Crematorium in
OL,16,FRhiwbina, north Cardiff.
