OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged theft of
OL,4,Chip replacements from crematorium
OL,6,FIt comes after there was "unauthorised
OL,7,Fentry" to the crematorium, during
OL,8,Fwhich two titanium orthopaedic joints
OL,9,Fwere taken from a recycling container,
OL,10,FCardiff Council said.
OL,12,FA council spokesperson has apologised
OL,13,Fto bereaved families and anyone who
OL,14,Fhas been upset by the revelation,
OL,15,Fsaying that they have put measures in
OL,16,Fplace to stop it happening in future.
