OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged theft of
OL,4,Chip replacements from crematorium
OL,6,FCardiff Council, which runs the
OL,7,Fcrematorium in Thornhill Road, said it
OL,8,Fkeeps the joints aside for recycling
OL,9,Fpurposes and sells them each year to
OL,10,Fraise money for various charities.
OL,12,FA Cardiff Council spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"On being made aware of an
OL,14,Funauthorised entry to the crematorium
OL,15,Fan investigation was conducted which
OL,16,Fled to a member of staff being
OL,17,Fsuspended and subsequently dismissed.
