OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged theft of
OL,4,Chip replacements from crematorium
OL,6,F"During this unauthorised visit two
OL,7,Ftitanium orthopaedic joints were taken
OL,8,Ffrom a recycling container. These
OL,9,Fjoints are kept aside for recycling
OL,10,Fpurposes and are sold by the council
OL,11,Fevery year raising money for various
OL,12,Fcharities. Once they are set aside for
OL,13,Frecycling, they are not traceable to
OL,14,Fany person.
OL,16,F"These matters were reported to the
OL,17,Fpolice, and we are helping them with
OL,18,Ftheir investigation.
