OL,6,F"We recognise the upset that this
OL,7,Fstory might cause the bereaved who
OL,8,Fhave used our services, but we want
OL,9,Fthem to know we have carried out a
OL,10,Fthorough investigation which has led
OL,11,Fto the dismissal of a member of staff.
