OL,3,CPolice investigate alleged theft of
OL,4,Chip replacements from crematorium
OL,6,F"It's important to the council that
OL,7,Four employees maintain the highest
OL,8,Fstandards which has clearly not
OL,9,Fhappened in this case. We would like
OL,10,Fto take this opportunity to apologise
OL,11,Fto anyone who is caused upset or
OL,12,Fconcern by this story and to assure
OL,13,Feveryone that measures have been put
OL,14,Fin place to stop anything like this
OL,15,Fhappening again."
OL,17,FA South Wales Police spokesperson
OL,18,Fsaid: "An investigation into the
OL,19,Falleged theft of orthopaedic implants
OL,20,Fat Thornhill Crematorium is currently
OL,21,Fongoing."
